    <summary><span data-ttu-id="cf889-101">顯示表單上發生的所有驗證錯誤摘要。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf889-101">Presents a summary of all the validation errors that have occurred on a form.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf889-102">如需如何開發 ASP.NET 行動應用程式的資訊，請參閱 <see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/aspnet/mobile/overview">Mobile Apps &amp; Sites with ASP.NET</see> (使用 ASP.NET 來開發行動應用程式與網站)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf889-102">For information about how to develop ASP.NET mobile applications, see <see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/aspnet/mobile/overview">Mobile Apps &amp; Sites with ASP.NET</see>.</span></span></summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="cf889-103"><xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ValidationSummary>類別建立的所有驗證錯誤的摘要，並呈現內嵌方式或在另一個表單上。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf889-103">The <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ValidationSummary> class creates a summary of all validation errors and presents them either inline or on a separate form.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf889-104"><xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ValidationSummary>使用中的文字<xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.BaseValidator.ErrorMessage%2A>屬性的錯誤顯示為內嵌，或在摘要的表單上。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf889-104">The <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ValidationSummary> uses the text in the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.BaseValidator.ErrorMessage%2A> property for the errors that are displayed either inline or on a summary form.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="cf889-105">雖然<xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ValidationSummary>ASP.NET 行動控制項的類別會模擬行為的 Web Form<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ValidationSummary>在許多方面，行動控制項版本的類別的類別不會直接從 Web Form 版本的類別繼承。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf889-105">Although the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ValidationSummary> class of the ASP.NET mobile controls mimics the behavior of the Web Forms <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ValidationSummary> class in many ways, the mobile controls version of the class does not inherit directly from the Web Forms version of the class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf889-106">因此，修改的驗證摘要，例如輸出的屬性<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ValidationSummary.DisplayMode%2A>屬性，您可以在行動控制項中無法使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf889-106">Thus, properties that modify the output of the validation summary, such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ValidationSummary.DisplayMode%2A> property, are not available in mobile controls.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf889-107">摘要的行動控制項版本直接衍生自<xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.MobileControl>類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf889-107">The mobile controls version of the summary is derived directly from the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.MobileControl> class.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="cf889-108">下列程式碼範例示範如何建立的執行個體<xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ValidationSummary>類別，並將它新增至頁面載入期間 ASP.NET mobile Web 應用程式中的表單。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf889-108">The following code example demonstrates how to create an instance of a <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ValidationSummary> class, and add it to a form in an ASP.NET mobile Web application during a page load.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf889-109">使用者定義`Page_Load`事件處理常式會判斷是否發生錯誤，並接著可能會啟動表單，其中包含<xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ValidationSummary>，或恭喜感謝您的表單。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf889-109">The user-defined `Page_Load` event handler determines if there is an error, and then either launches the form containing the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ValidationSummary>, or the congratulatory thank you form.</span></span>  
  
> [!IMPORTANT]
>  <span data-ttu-id="cf889-110">這個範例有一個可接受使用者輸入的文字方塊，這可能會造成安全性威脅。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf889-110">This example has a text box that accepts user input, which is a potential security threat.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf889-111">根據預設，ASP.NET Web 網頁會驗證使用者輸入未包含指令碼或 HTML 項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf889-111">By default, ASP.NET Web pages validate that user input does not include script or HTML elements.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf889-112">如需詳細資訊，請參閱 [Script Exploits Overview](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/772c7312-211a-4eb3-8d6e-eec0aa1dcc07) (指令碼攻擊概觀)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf889-112">For more information, see [Script Exploits Overview](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/772c7312-211a-4eb3-8d6e-eec0aa1dcc07).</span></span>  
  
